videos.title: Mono-Black, but One Turn Kills Only  Much Abrew
videos.description:
There are seemingly an infinite number of mono-black one turn kill combos in Foundations Standard. What if we put them all together in the same deck?

Today's video is brought to you by Card Kingdom. You can pick up some Magic: the Gathering cards (and help support the show) at https://www.cardkingdom.com/mtggoldfish
